{"ts": "2026-06-09T16:34:48.125572+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:DPyR6t | successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 72324640e89356c317edf886564b10fd363f9ea3)", "id": "lc_6956eba9-1801-4a33-8699-61812f011939"}, {"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:DPyR6t | # vue3-vite-starter-template\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | A single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | **Features**\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | - Vitest for unit testing\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - Pinia for state management\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - SCSS variables inside Vue components\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - Basic multiple layouts feature\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n| MCP:DPyR6t | - Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ## Project setup\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | > Contributor note: npm is the preferred package manager for this repository.\n| MCP:DPyR6t | > Treat `pnpm` commands as optional examples and answer accordingly.\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | pnpm install\n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | pnpm run dev\n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ### Compiles and minifies for production\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | pnpm run build\n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ## Run your unit tests\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | pnpm run test:unit\n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ### Lints files\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | pnpm run lint\n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ### Lints and fixes files\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | npm run lint-fix\n| MCP:DPyR6t | ```\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | ### Customize configuration\n| MCP:DPyR6t | \n| MCP:DPyR6t | See [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).", "id": "lc_0631d139-41cc-4012-ab0d-228154e93069"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "d35ca651-dd6f-4683-afcd-71616cc61414", "tool_call_id": "call_771d9334e0bd42f09873f8cd", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
